<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/3 (Thu)Why is Russia invading Ukraine and what does Putin want? /Warren Buffett's Investment Strategy(Host: Louie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=595&amp;p=618#p618"><![CDATA[
Why is Russia invading Ukraine and what does Putin want? /Warren Buffett's Investment Strategy<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1<br />Why is Russia invading Ukraine and what does Putin want? <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zuoqLNK8_mc">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zuoqLNK8_mc</a><!-- m --><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56720589">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-56720589</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.How much do you know about the relationship of Ukraine, Russia, NATO and USA?<br />2.Just before the warfare between Ukraine and Russia recently, do you think it’s still possible to see warfare between major countries nowadays in the world? Why?<br />3.Ever since Russia launched the incursion to Ukraine on 2/24, NATO and its allies, including Japan, even Taiwan only proclaimed to economically sanction Russia. Biden even swore to let the intruder pay the most severe cost. Do you think this would work to daunt Putin’s progress? <br />4.Who is to blame for this warfare? If you were a Ukrainian living in the west part, will you support Zelensky’s policy to de-Russianize and to seek for joining NATO?<br />5.Will you flee from Taiwan when you see a war is looming? What will you do?<br /><br />Session 2 <br />Warren Buffett's Investment Strategy<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.fool.com/investing/how-to-invest/famous-investors/warren-buffett-investments/">https://www.fool.com/investing/how-to-i ... vestments/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Do you invest in stock market? Since when? Does your investment make you big fortune, or make you lose money?<br />2.What are your investment tools to manage your fortune? Time Deposit （定存）in banks? Bond（債券）? Real estates? Stocks? Mutual Fund （共同基金）? Foreign exchange? Precious metals? Futures Market? What is your portfolio （投資組合） for these investment tools?<br />3.What is your idea about good/healthy notions in stock investment?<br />4.How do you think about Warren Buffett’s investment strategy cited in this article?<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Feb 26, 2022 4:40 pm</p><hr />
